    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The bug with the pagination not sent with the analytics has been solved in 2.2.0-beta.1 ([related PR](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/pull/2337)). Also the `triggerOnUIInteraction` option is for triggering the analytics before we change page. Internally the widget is conservative and will not call the hook if the state hasn't changed.",
